Package: logr-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: logr (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: customizable logging library for C/C++ - development
 logr provides log file formatting and rotation in a similar fashion to Java's
 java.util.logging package or Python's logging module.

